    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You let your shield absorb some of the damage from a fall.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Shield Focus, base attack bonus +6 or fighter level 4th.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>When you fall 10 or more feet, you can direct half of the falling damage you would take to your shield. This damage ignores the shield's hardness.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 5 stamina points to utilize your shield's hardness when directing falling damage to it. (See page 18.)",
